00:46:23,019 --> 00:46:32,019
[SPEAKER_04] Dole u temelju. Brše se prijem samo u granje stroja.

650
00:46:32,019 --> 00:46:36,019
[SPEAKER_04] Ovo morate iskopati. Oglomu poličinu materijala.

651
00:46:36,019 --> 00:46:41,019
[SPEAKER_04] U tu ogromu poličinu materijala morate izbastiti.

652
00:46:42,019 --> 00:46:51,019
[SPEAKER_04] Onda morate staviti za ovakve agregate najmanje 700 do 1000 kubika armiranog betona sa aditivima.

653
00:46:51,019 --> 00:46:57,019
[SPEAKER_04] I na to ćete postaviti stroj koji je visok 100 metara, čija je gondola nazen 100 metara.

654
00:46:57,019 --> 00:47:01,019
[SPEAKER_04] I još imate gore jednog 70 do 80 metara u opacu.

655
00:47:01,019 --> 00:47:02,019
[SPEAKER_02] 90.

656
00:47:02,019 --> 00:47:03,019
[SPEAKER_04] 90.

657
00:47:03,019 --> 00:47:05,019
[SPEAKER_04] Znači 180 metara.

658
00:47:05,019 --> 00:47:12,019
[SPEAKER_04] I taj stroj, kad stoji, kad stoji, ne mora ništa raditi.

659
00:47:12,019 --> 00:47:14,019
[SPEAKER_04] On vibrira 30.

660
00:47:16,019 --> 00:47:19,019
[SPEAKER_04] Oneti vjetra, uzrokuju naprezanja u černčnoj konstrukciji.

661
00:47:19,019 --> 00:47:21,019
[SPEAKER_04] I sve se dobro nasi na to.

662
00:47:21,019 --> 00:47:25,019
[SPEAKER_04] I to se danas može mjeriti.

663
00:47:25,019 --> 00:47:27,019
[SPEAKER_04] U cijelim, u tim parkovima.

664
00:47:27,019 --> 00:47:29,019
[SPEAKER_04] Postavlje se zimno senzori okolo.

665
00:47:29,019 --> 00:47:31,019
[SPEAKER_04] Pusti se u tog polje.

666
00:47:31,019 --> 00:47:33,019
[SPEAKER_04] Kad radi, kad ne radi.

667
00:47:33,019 --> 00:47:35,019
[SPEAKER_04] I mjeruje se poremećanje.

668
00:47:35,019 --> 00:47:36,019
[SPEAKER_04] Jel vam li to ništa prije to?

669
00:47:36,019 --> 00:47:37,019
[SPEAKER_04] Šta se događa?

670
00:47:37,019 --> 00:47:39,019
[SPEAKER_04] Ništo nije ni prško.

671
00:47:39,019 --> 00:47:40,019
[SPEAKER_04] Možete to počitati.

672
00:47:40,019 --> 00:47:41,019
[SPEAKER_04] Samo počitati.

673
00:47:41,019 --> 00:47:44,019
[SPEAKER_04] O tom sumarnom utjecaju na okolič.

674
00:47:45,019 --> 00:47:47,019
[SPEAKER_04] Samo jedna elektrana.

675
00:47:47,019 --> 00:47:48,019
[SPEAKER_04] A vi zamislite sad.

676
00:47:48,019 --> 00:47:49,019
[SPEAKER_04] Ovi nam planinjaju.

677
00:47:49,019 --> 00:47:51,019
[SPEAKER_04] Znate koliko elektrana?

678
00:47:51,019 --> 00:47:52,019
[SPEAKER_04] Više nego što je sad.

679
00:47:52,019 --> 00:47:56,019
[SPEAKER_04] Snažna elektronizacija se usao u osnih recibovi.

680
00:47:56,019 --> 00:47:58,019
[SPEAKER_04] Još je odgovorit na jedno pitanje.

681
00:47:58,019 --> 00:47:59,019
[SPEAKER_04] Zašto je sva ta halbuka?

682
00:47:59,019 --> 00:48:02,019
[SPEAKER_04] Svi su se zapoticajali.

683
00:48:02,019 --> 00:48:04,019
[SPEAKER_04] Zapoticaje su se javili.

684
00:48:04,019 --> 00:48:06,019
[SPEAKER_04] Sada, antenutno.

685
00:48:06,019 --> 00:48:09,019
[SPEAKER_04] Ako mi ne vedete, možete pogugljati.

686
00:48:09,019 --> 00:48:14,019
[SPEAKER_04] Urad za obnovljivje izvoje energije i kogeneraciji.

687
00:48:14,019 --> 00:48:15,019
[SPEAKER_04] vladino tijelo.

688
00:48:15,019 --> 00:48:17,019
[SPEAKER_04] Samo vam ima trenutno.

689
00:48:17,019 --> 00:48:23,019
[SPEAKER_04] Elektroprigrada svojih koje potiče 280 firmi.

690
00:48:23,019 --> 00:48:33,019
[SPEAKER_04] Javno podruzeće elektroprigrada HZHV ima 211.

691
00:48:33,019 --> 00:48:36,019
[SPEAKER_04] Samo javno podruzeće elektroprigrada.

692
00:48:36,019 --> 00:48:49,019
